Write a program in PROLOG to implement generate_fib(N,T) where T represents the  Nth term of the Fibonacci series.


generate_fib(1, 0).
generate_fib(2, 1).
generate_fib(N, T) :-
    N > 2,
    N1 is N - 1,
    N2 is N - 2,
    generate_fib(N1, T1),
    generate_fib(N2, T2),
    T is T1 + T2.

% Query: ?- generate_fib(7, T).  → T = 8
